Introduction

  The {{{jdtaus-core-api/project-summary.html}Core API artifact}} provides
  the jDTAUS Core's {{{jdtaus-core-api/apidocs/index.html}programming interface}}
  to services like task monitoring and modular object management and
  configuration. Whenever that artifact is used at compile time, an application
  assembler needs to provide additional runtime artifacts for proper operation
  as shown below.

*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
|| <<Artifact>>     || <<Description>>                                        ||
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-client-container/index.html} jDTAUS Core RI Client Container}} | <<<Container>>>, <<<Model>>> and <<<Context>>> reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-client-container/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-servlet-container/index.html} jDTAUS Core RI Servlet Container}} | Web application integration reference implementation. (Only needed when integrating with web applications.) {{{jdtaus-core-servlet-container/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-jdk-logging/project-summary.html} jDTAUS Core RI JDK 1.4 Logging}} | JDK 1.4 logging reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-jdk-logging/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-log4j-logging/project-summary.html} jDTAUS Core RI Log4J Logging}} | Log4J logging reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-log4j-logging/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-commons-logging/project-summary.html} jDTAUS Core RI Commons Logging}} | Commons logging reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-commons-logging/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-task-monitor/project-summary.html} jDTAUS Core RI Task Monitor}} | Task monitoring reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-task-monitor/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-memory-manager/project-summary.html} jDTAUS Core RI Memory Manager}} | Runtime reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-memory-manager/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-jdk14-executor/project-summary.html} jDTAUS Core RI JDK 1.4 Executor}} | JDK 1.4 executor reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-jdk14-executor/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{jdtaus-core-application-logger/project-summary.html} jDTAUS Core RI Application Logger}} | Application logger reference implementation. {{{jdtaus-core-application-logger/apidocs/}See Javadoc}}|
*-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+

  <<Note:>> The logging implementations are exclusive. Only one of the artifacts
  is allowed to be put on an application's classpath.

